transcription.cn: 我就是照亮普雷顿之心的火焰。
transcription.en: I am the flame that lights up the heart of Preton.

cn.zh-Hans: 我就是照亮普雷顿之心的火焰。
cn.en: I am the flame that lights up the heart of Preton.

transcription.cn: 为了保护你，无论什么时候，我都会站出来。
transcription.en: I will protect you whenever you need me.

cn.ko: 당신을 지키기 위해, 언제든 나설 준비가 되어 있어요.
cn.zh-Hans: 为了保护你，无论什么时候，我都会站出来。
cn.en: I will protect you whenever you need me.

transcription.cn: （呼）艾卡，你能行的，加油。
transcription.en: (Phew) You got this, Eika. Keep it up.

cn.zh-Hans: （呼）艾卡，你能行的，加油。
cn.en: (Phew) You got this, Eika. Keep it up.

transcription.cn: 火花很容易被扑灭，所以，必须全力以赴地燃烧。
transcription.en: Sparks are easily extinguished. You must burn with all your might.

cn.ko: 불꽃은 쉽게 꺼지니까 온 힘을 다해 태워야 해요.
cn.zh-Hans: 火花很容易被扑灭，所以，必须全力以赴地燃烧。
cn.en: Sparks are easily extinguished. You must burn with all your might.

transcription.cn: 相信最后的胜利，要从相信自己开始。
transcription.en: Achieving victory begins with believing in yourself.

cn.ko: 최후의 승리를 원한다면, 나 자신부터 믿어보세요.
cn.zh-Hans: 相信最后的胜利，要从相信自己开始。
cn.en: Believing in the final victory starts with believing in yourself.

transcription.cn: 来的正是时候！
transcription.en: About time!

cn.zh-Hans: 来的正是时候！
cn.en: About time!

transcription.cn: 尽情燃烧吧！
transcription.en: Burn with all your might!

cn.zh-Hans: 尽情燃烧吧！
cn.en: Burn with all your might!

transcription.cn: 正面对决，还是弦化躲避？决定好了吗？
transcription.en: Face-off or flee? Have you decided?

cn.ko: 정면 대결할까요, 아니면 스트링화로 피하실래요? 결정했나요?
cn.zh-Hans: 正面对决，还是弦化躲避？决定好了吗？
cn.en: Face-to-face confrontation, or evasion? Have you decided yet?

transcription.cn: 现在，我就是即将迫近的焚风！
transcription.en: I am the foehn wind that approaches!

cn.ko: 지금부터 전 모든 걸 휩쓸 열풍이 될 거예요!
cn.zh-Hans: 现在，我就是即将迫近的焚风！
cn.en: I am the foehn wind that approaches!

transcription.cn: 逆弦之火绝不烧灼友人，只会席卷一切对手！
transcription.en: The flames of reverstring will never scorch an ally, but will sweep away all enemies!

cn.ko: 역현의 불꽃은 절대 친구를 태우지 않죠. 오직 모든 적만을 휩쓸 거예요!
cn.zh-Hans: 逆弦之火绝不烧灼友人，只会席卷一切对手！
cn.en: The flames of reverstring will never scorch an ally, but will sweep away all enemies!

transcription.cn: 给我统统上天！
transcription.en: Send them flying!

cn.zh-Hans: 给我统统上天！
cn.en: Give it all to me!

transcription.cn: 该结束啦，我还要去参加乐队呢。
transcription.en: Let's wrap it up. I have band practice.

cn.ko: 이제 끝내야겠어요. 밴드 연습을 가야 하거든요.
cn.zh-Hans: 该结束啦，我还要去参加乐队呢。
cn.en: Let's wrap it up. I have band practice.

transcription.cn: 想回归日常的话，那就放弃战斗吧。
transcription.en: Surrender if you want everything to return to normal.

cn.zh-Hans: 想回归日常的话，那就放弃战斗吧。
cn.en: Surrender if you want everything to return to normal.

transcription.cn: 结果我赢了，又强又厉害。
transcription.en: I win. I'm amazing.

cn.zh-Hans: 结果我赢了，又强又厉害。
cn.en: In the end I won, I was strong and powerful.

transcription.cn: 不要阻拦艾卡！是这种感觉吧？
transcription.en: Don't stop Eika! Did I say that right?

cn.zh-Hans: 不要阻拦艾卡！是这种感觉吧？
cn.en: Don't stop Eika! Did I say that right?

transcription.cn: 回去换一身衣服再来吧。
transcription.en: Go change your clothes.

cn.zh-Hans: 回去换一身衣服再来吧。
cn.en: Go change your clothes.

transcription.cn: 那就祝您身体健康，再见咯！
transcription.en: Wishing you good health, see ya!

cn.zh-Hans: 那就祝您身体健康，再见咯！
cn.en: Wishing you good health, see ya!

transcription.cn: 马上就能暖和起来了。
transcription.en: You'll warm up in no time.

cn.zh-Hans: 马上就能暖和起来了。
cn.en: !NoTextFound!

transcription.cn: 没关系，不就是一时的输赢嘛，抛在身后吧。
transcription.en: You win some, you lose some. Let it go.

cn.zh-Hans: 没关系，不就是一时的输赢嘛，抛在身后吧。
cn.en: You win some, you lose some. Let it go.

transcription.cn: 赢了！哈哈哈……啊，又有点得意忘形了……
transcription.en: We won! Ha-ha-ha... I got a bit carried away again...

cn.zh-Hans: 赢了！哈哈哈……啊，又有点得意忘形了……
cn.en: We won! Ha-ha-ha... I got a bit carried away again...

transcription.cn: 咱们做的已经足够多了，真的。
transcription.en: We tried our best.

cn.zh-Hans: 咱们做的已经足够多了，真的。
cn.en: We tried our best. Really.

transcription.cn: 我就是——无敌的女高中生！这次就记好吧！
transcription.en: I am the invincible high school student! Remember me!

cn.ko: 제가 바로... 무적의 여고생이죠! 이번엔 제대로 기억하세요!
cn.zh-Hans: 我就是——无敌的女高中生！这次就记好吧！
cn.en: I am the invincible high school student! Remember me!

transcription.cn: 咱们一起走吧？
transcription.en: Shall we move together?

cn.zh-Hans: 咱们一起走吧？
cn.en: Shall we move together?

transcription.cn: 得耐心等待时机才行。
transcription.en: Patience. Wait for an opening.

cn.zh-Hans: 得耐心等待时机才行。
cn.en: Patience. Wait for an opening.

transcription.cn: 接到指令，得撤退了。
transcription.en: I've been ordered to retreat.

cn.zh-Hans: 接到指令，得撤退了。
cn.en: I've been ordered to retreat.

transcription.cn: 非常感谢你！
transcription.en: Thank you very much!

cn.zh-Hans: 非常感谢你！
cn.en: Thank you very much!

transcription.cn: 你真的真——的很不错！
transcription.en: You've done really, really well!

cn.zh-Hans: 你真的真——的很不错！
cn.en: You've done really, really well!

transcription.cn: 那就这样吧。
transcription.en: So be it.

cn.zh-Hans: 那就这样吧。
cn.en: So be it.

transcription.cn: 这样可不行。
transcription.en: That won't cut it.

cn.zh-Hans: 这样可不行。
cn.en: That won't cut it.

transcription.cn: 抱、抱歉……
transcription.en: S-Sorry...

cn.zh-Hans: 抱、抱歉……
cn.en: S-Sorry...

transcription.cn: 啊，你好。
transcription.en: Oh, hello.

cn.zh-Hans: 啊，你好。
cn.en: Oh, hello.

transcription.cn: 卡拉彼丘。
transcription.en: Strinova.

cn.zh-Hans: 卡拉彼丘。

transcription.cn: 有些比主武器还要好用。
transcription.en: Some are even more useful than primary weapons.

cn.ko: 주 무기보다 더 쓸만한 것도 있어요.
cn.zh-Hans: 有些比主武器还要好用。
cn.en: Some are even more useful than primary weapons.
